#!/usr/bin/env python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
r"""
sonar_calc_singlefile_v1_0.py

Clean single-file public implementation wrapper for SONAR-Calc v1.0.

Important
---------
This file does not rewrite SONAR/H-AEND scientific rules. It embeds the frozen
manuscript-parity modules as source text and writes them into a local runtime
module directory before execution. Network construction, reversible H-AEND, and
destructive H-AEND are executed through those frozen implementations.

The wrapper adds:
1. a single central params file;
2. per-protein multiprocessing controlled by n_cpu;
3. standardized report export:
   - SONAR Core Report v1.0 = 44 fields
   - SONAR Extended Label Matrix v1.0 = 87 fields
4. atlas-scale right-censor handling for no-damage destructive sweeps.

Run
---
python sonar_calc_singlefile_v1_0.py --params params_sonar_calc_manuscript_v1_0.csv
"""

